This directory is intended to contain the default profiles for 
the 3.0 utilities.  You can use these profiles either by copying
them to ~/.DjVu/., or by specifying the --config option at runtime.

TEST HISTORY:

02/29/00, Patrick Haffner
--------------------------------
Profiles tested for visual aspect:
clean100
clean300
scan100
scan200
scan300
scan600
draw300
invert300
fine-invert300
fine-text300
manuscript200
manuscript300

Profiles just tested for compression rate (just look at the file size, not the output):
aggressive300: always smaller than other profiles


